data.name: label2.Text
data.value: To put your mouse in DFU mode, do the following: 1. Turn the mouse off. 2. Disconnect the wireless receiver from the included micro-USB cable. 3. Hold down M3 (middle-click) + DPI on the mouse. 4. Plug in the mouse with the included micro-USB cable while performing (3).

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Programs such as NZXT CAM, Corsair iCUE, Razer Cortex, that monitor hardware devices can potentially interfere with the update process. Please close/exit out of such programs/tasks before proceeding.
